1. Start local vLLM
BioPlotAgents assumes a local vLLM server exposing an OpenAI-compatible API. In src/llm_langchain.py the default configuration is:

llm = ChatOpenAI(
    openai_api_base="http://12.12.12.62:8000/v1",
    openai_api_key="EMPTY",
    model="qwen2.5-coder-7b",
    temperature=0.2,
    max_tokens=512,
)
Adjust openai_api_base and model to match your environment.

2. Install Python dependencies
Inside your container or virtual environment:

pip install -r requirements.txt
A minimal set of packages includes:

pandas
seaborn
matplotlib
langchain
langchain-openai
langgraph
pdf2image
PyPDF2
pydantic
scikit-learn
Pillow
numpy
vllm (server side)
